 Apocalypse walked around the corner and bumped into Drillbit. "She is dead. 
But there are worse things. We must not let Megatron get command of the 
predacons. Please side with me against him. From now on I take orders from 
you and so does the rest of my troops. Thats 7men or more." he bowed to his 
new leader. He knew he would be useful there.
